---
title: Peržiūrėti keliones — sequence diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor N as Naudotojas

  participant TLV as TripListView<br/>«boundary»
  participant TDV as TripDetailsView<br/>«boundary»

  participant TLC as TripListController<br/>«control»

  participant Trip as Trip<br/>«entity»

  participant DB as DB

  N->>TLV: atidaryti mano keliones
  TLV->>TLC: getTrips(userId)
  TLC->>DB: query(Trip by userId)
  DB-->>TLC: tripsData
  TLC-->>TLV: trips
  TLV-->>N: rodyti kelionių sąrašą

  N->>TLV: pasirinkti kelionę
  TLV->>TLC: getTripDetails(tripId)
  TLC->>Trip: load(tripId)
  Trip-->>TLC: trip
  TLC-->>TDV: showTrip(trip)
  TDV-->>N: rodyti kelionės detales

  opt Filtravimas pagal statusą/datą
    N->>TLV: filtruoti(status, dateRange)
    TLV->>TLC: filterTrips(criteria)
    TLC->>DB: query(Trip by criteria)
    DB-->>TLC: filteredTrips
    TLC-->>TLV: filteredTrips
    TLV-->>N: atnaujintas sąrašas
  end
